Installed-Size: 60
Depends: python:any, python-milter (>= 0.9.3), python-spf (>= 2.0), lsb-base, adduser
Suggests: postfix (>= 2.3) | sendmail (>= 8.13)
Section: mail
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/sdgathman/milter/
Description: RFC 7208 compliant SPF Milter for Sendmail and Postfix
 A Python mail filter to add Received-SPF headers and reject forged mail.
 Rejection policy is configured via sendmail access file. Updated for RFC
 4408/7208 compliance.
